              <table width="100%" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="5" border="0"><tr><td valign="top"><img src="../modules/mod_jphotostack/tmpl/images/jphotostack.png" border="0" /></td>
              <td valign="top" style="padding-left:60px;">
                <p>J Photostack Show images as gallery from different folder. Folders are pretty much static and which are located under modules mod_jphotostack/tmpl/albums . Up to ten folder can be added for image show. In each folder there is thumb folder to view thumb image in category view. From module parameter there is option to configure each of ten entries. Module parameters are given below:</p>
                <p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Name [1]:</li>
                        <li>Description [1]:</li>
                        <li>Thum [1]:</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
              </td></tr></table>
            </td></tr>
            </table>
            ]]>
